<title>lmạ bsẖtm qlby byḥzn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lmạ bạsẖtm qlby byḥzn wyswʿ bybqy̱ zʿlạn
 lmạ bạsẖtm bạsẖʿr ạ̹ny mgẖlwb whzmny ạlsẖyṭạn
 (ạ̉ʿml ạ̹yh? qwlwạ yạ ṣḥạby
 ạ̉ʿml ạ̹yh? qwlwạ ly qwạm)2
 (ṣly llrb yswʿ wqwl lh ạ̉nạ gẖlṭạn
 ạḥfẓ ly bạb sẖfạyfy wạḥrṣ ạllsạn)2
 (wlmạ ạ̉rkʿ wạ̉ṣly wạ̉ṭlb ạlgẖfrạn
 hyryḥ ḥạlaⁿạ wạ̉sẖʿr bạlạ̉mạn)2</lyrics>
</song>